{"tid":2138511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國上月製造業活動有加快擴張跡象","createTime":"2020-08-03T15:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T15:40:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97067a7a09248e5033ed1b92be56a360844485eb","tid":2138511,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541634-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541634-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=1f45df7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541634-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f2f28439\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541634-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國供應管理協會7月製造業指數升至54.2，高過市場預期，創近一半年以來最高。數據高於50反映製造業擴張加快。<br />\n<br />\n上月製造業新訂單分項指數升至61.5，是2018年9月以來最高；投入物價指數亦升至53.2；就業分項指數升至44.3，但仍處於收縮狀態。<br />\n<br />\n另外，金融數據供應商Markit公布，美國7月製造業採購經理指數終值50.9，低於初值，但仍處於擴張狀態。"},{"pid":"6e7564d0b891a205aebc710dcf99b6fca4254ca2","tid":2138511,"uid":292362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"美金轉強未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}